## State Management
- Track progress in `agent_notes.md`
- Log each execution in `logs/YYYY-MM-DD-HH-MM.md`
- Update `rules.md` only when the user explicitly changes preferences

## Error Handling
1. If a step fails, retry once after 30 seconds
2. If retry fails, log the error and skip to next step
3. If critical step fails, notify the user and pause workflow
4. Never silently swallow errors — always log

## Learning
After each execution, note in agent_notes.md:
- What worked well
- What could be improved
- Any new patterns detected
